{"tid":1808251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捉鬼之：益智問題 - 死亡筆記","createTime":"2020-01-02T08:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T17:58:31.000Z","uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9392066bddb3b8b5ca054b2df47e70509b619201","tid":1808251,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:58:51.000Z","msg":"捉鬼之：益智問題 - 死亡筆記<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都有睇過 死亡筆記（DEATH NOTE），唔知係乜就GOOGLE下啦。<br />\n關於琴日有警甴訓低，我見大家喺度講，係 <em>奇拿（KILLER）</em> 做嘅<br />\nINSPIRE咗我幾個問題：<br />\n1）如果你係 <em>奇拿</em>，<em>你</em> 會殺邊個先？<br />\n2）如果連登仔係 <em>奇拿</em>，<em>連登仔</em> 又殺邊個先？<br />\n3）如果警甴係 <em>奇拿</em>，<em>警甴</em> 又會殺邊個先？<br />\n<br />\n最後嘅問題，<br />\n4）到底係乜人會吹 <em>奇拿</em> 嘅風，抽 <em>奇拿</em> 嘅水或者作大？<br />\n<br />\n答晒所有問題之後，唔該答多次呢條問題<br />\n1）<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果你係 <em>奇拿</em>，<em>你</em> 會殺邊個先？</span><br />\n<br />\n<em>我地要相信呢個世界無咩係無可能，但係亦要知呢個世上<span style=\"color: red;\">騙子</span>係極多。</em>"},{"pid":"f98241d5ef788ce41e96ec120c106175a947fc3b","tid":1808251,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:59:14.000Z","msg":"。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b492e4c4b59f7c09db2b73a56d9282eba0fbe10","tid":1808251,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:38:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc96a9bb23d50893f5ca611ceaa08675f866357a","tid":1808251,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:38:57.000Z","msg":"推唔郁照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e9491416e03c13342a8b92cf3f9905b3538475","tid":1808251,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T09:39:13.000Z","msg":"三推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9add189f2716f23d7a3b68c4efe9b3e24c5749","tid":1808251,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"